txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Great membranes from the slugs surrounding Gabilshathûr. Delivery of the items should be made to Avar at the dwarf-outpost.
'Slugs have a thick membrane that does not burn very well. We'd like some of these.'
The dwarves at Gabilshathûr await a delivery of great membranes to be made to Avar.
Deliver the great membranes to Avar at Gabilshathûr in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver great membranes from the slugs surrounding Gabilshathûr to Avar at the dwarf-outpost.
Wanted: Great membranes from the slugs surrounding Gabilshathûr.
